sequenceDiagram
    %% ── 类型 1: 简单视频生成 ──
    actor User as 👤 User
    participant FE as 🌐 Browser (Tab 1)
    participant Server as ⚡ FastAPI Server
    participant SP as SimpleVideoPipeline
    participant API as AgnesVideoAPI
    participant Agnes as Agnes Video API

    rect rgb(40, 50, 80)
        Note over User,Agnes: 类型 1: 简单视频生成 (Simple Video)

        User->>FE: 输入 prompt + 选择模式 + 参数
        FE->>Server: POST /api/tasks/simple<br/>{prompt, mode, duration, seed...}

        Server->>SP: new SimpleVideoPipeline(api_key, task_id, dir_name)
        Server->>SP: asyncio.create_task(pipeline.run(state))

        SP->>SP: 创建 task_state.json (status=running)
        SP->>FE: WS progress: init

        alt mode = t2v (文生视频)
            SP->>API: submit_video(prompt, refs=[])
        else mode = i2v/ti2vid (图生视频)
            SP->>API: submit_video(prompt, refs=[ref_image])
        else mode = keyframes (关键帧)
            SP->>API: submit_video(prompt, refs=[first_frame, end_frame])
        end

        API->>Agnes: POST /v1/videos (mode=t2v/ti2vid/keyframes)
        Agnes-->>API: {video_id: "xxx"}
        API-->>SP: video_id

        SP->>SP: 保存 task.json (video_id)

        loop 轮询 (每15s)
            SP->>API: wait_for_video(video_id)
            API->>Agnes: GET /agnesapi?video_id=xxx
            Agnes-->>API: {status: "processing", progress: 45%}
            SP->>FE: WS progress: video_gen (running, 45%)
        end

        Agnes-->>API: {status: "completed", video_url: "..."}
        API-->>SP: VideoOutput(url)
        SP->>SP: 下载视频 → final_video.mp4
        SP->>SP: 更新 task_state.json (status=completed)
        SP->>FE: WS progress: done (completed, 100%)
        FE->>User: 显示视频预览 + 下载按钮
    end

    ---

    %% ── 类型 2: 创意长视频生成 ──
    rect rgb(60, 40, 80)
        Note over User,Agnes: 类型 2: 创意长视频生成 (Creative Video, 增强)

        User->>FE: 输入创意描述 + 配置音频
        FE->>Server: POST /api/tasks/creative<br/>{idea, style, audio_config...}

        Server->>SP: new CreativeVideoPipeline(...)
        Server->>SP: asyncio.create_task(pipeline.run(state))

        SP->>SP: Step 0: 图片分析 (如有参考图)
        SP->>SP: Step 1: 故事生成 (Screenwriter.develop_story)
        SP->>SP: Step 2: 角色参考图 (Screenwriter → AgnesImageAPI)
        SP->>SP: Step 3: 脚本编写 (Screenwriter.write_script + narration)
        SP->>SP: Step 3.5: 尾帧提示词 (keyframes 模式)
        SP->>SP: Step 3.6: 预生成尾帧 (AgnesImageAPI)
        SP->>SP: Step 4: 视频生成 (AgnesVideoAPI × N scenes)

        Note over SP: === 新增：音频字幕步骤 ===
        SP->>SP: Step 5: 音频+字幕合成

        loop 每个场景 scene_i
            SP->>TTSEngine: EdgeTTSEngine.generate(narration_text[i])
            TTSEngine-->>SP: (audio_path, sub_maker with cues)

            SP->>SubtitleGen: SubtitleGenerator.cues_to_srt(cues)
            SubtitleGen-->>SP: subtitle.srt

            SP->>SubtitleGen: overlay_subtitles_to_video(video_path, srt, style)
            SubtitleGen-->>SP: scene_i_with_subtitle.mp4

            SP->>Concatenator: 合成 scene_i 的音频+视频
            Concatenator-->>SP: scene_i_final.mp4
        end

        SP->>SP: Step 6: 视频拼接
        SP->>Concatenator: concat_with_audio(scene_files)
        Concatenator-->>SP: final_video.mp4

        SP->>FE: WS progress: done
        FE->>User: 显示视频预览
    end

    ---

    %% ── 类型 3: 稿件长视频生成 ──
    rect rgb(40, 70, 70)
        Note over User,Agnes: 类型 3: 稿件长视频生成 (Manuscript Video)

        User->>FE: 输入长文本 + 配置音频
        FE->>Server: POST /api/tasks/manuscript<br/>{manuscript_text, audio_config...}

        Server->>MP: new ManuscriptVideoPipeline(...)
        Server->>MP: asyncio.create_task(pipeline.run(state))

        MP->>MP: Step 1: 文本预处理
        Note over MP: 按换行符拆分为 N 个段落

        loop 每个段落 para_i
            MP->>Screenwriter: generate_scene_prompt(para_i.text)
            Screenwriter-->>MP: scene_prompt_i
            MP->>MP: 存储 scene_prompt 到 state
        end

        MP->>MP: Step 2: 场景聚类判断
        Note over MP: 相邻段落 scene_prompt 语义相似 → 同场景

        loop 每个段落/场景组
            alt 同场景连续段落
                MP->>API: submit_video(keyframes, [first, end])
            else 独立场景
                MP->>API: submit_video(t2v, prompt)
            end
            API-->>MP: video_id
            MP->>API: wait_for_video(video_id)
            API-->>MP: video_file
        end

        Note over MP: Step 3: 音频+字幕合成
        loop 每个段落 para_i
            MP->>TTSEngine: EdgeTTSEngine.generate(para_i.text)
            TTSEngine-->>MP: (audio_path, sub_maker)
            MP->>SubtitleGen: cues_to_srt → overlay
            SubtitleGen-->>MP: para_i_final.mp4
        end

        MP->>MP: Step 4: 拼接
        MP->>Concatenator: concat_with_audio(all_paras)
        Concatenator-->>MP: final_video.mp4

        MP->>FE: WS progress: done
        FE->>User: 显示视频预览
    end
